{"tid":1529191,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"9月2日就開學喇，有啲野想各位中學手足留意返","createTime":"2019-09-01T16:33:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T02:55:32.000Z","uid":19326,"like":81,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"34867a5844222cd5b6324c9c8daad12a31db8d6c","tid":1529191,"uid":19326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T16:33:57.000Z","msg":"無論你間學校係咩底咩色都好，有啲嘢真係要小心<br />\n<br />\n1. 學校老師極有可能借機會同大家討論反送中嘅事，希望各位手足要小心言詞，唔好透露自己曾經發夢，保障自己，所謂嘅學校其實係社會嘅縮影，尤其係啲打份工嘅仆街教畜，隨時賣左你搏取校長歡心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 啲濕鳩學校社工都要提防，唔好覺得佢係社工就放低戒心，啲仆街學校社工最叻係出賣求助人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要小心唔好透露自己曾經發夢，如果真係需要情緒輔導，要小心言語，盡可能講自己係受件事困擾，唔好透露曾經發夢<br />\n<br />\n3. 朋輩間，我相信各位手足會應對到<br />\n<br />\n4. 狗仔狗女方面，我個人認為唔流血嘅心靈攻擊比見血會有更有效，長期傷害嚟<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後，希望大家萬事小心，實踐九二共識<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可"},{"pid":"37c0bec5a4c598f43a1ca8414637d0459d114083","tid":1529191,"uid":60092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T16:34:51.000Z","msg":"聽俾中學生知"},{"pid":"8c137a19eb1ab426b61aded34d5a30b9bec2ae59","tid":1529191,"uid":166117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T16:35:23.000Z","msg":"推 真係要小心"},{"pid":"ab1f953f84c83ac1181df868cddc5c1b0ad6e2e4","tid":1529191,"uid":257422,